Package org.goplanit.utils.graph

Interface UntypedGraph<V extends Vertex,​E extends Edge>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<IdAble>, IdAble, ManagedId
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DirectedGraph<V,​E,​ES>, Graph<V,​E>, UntypedDirectedGraph<V,​E,​ES>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectedGraphImpl, GraphImpl, UntypedDirectedGraphImpl, UntypedGraphImpl
    public interface UntypedGraph<V extends Vertex,​E extends Edge>
extends ManagedId
    A graph interface consisting of vertices and edges without specifying a concrete container type to access them. Only generic method signatures in this base interface.
    Author:
    markr
